                <h1>"Discover the Magic of Parallax Effect in Web Design"</h1>
                <p>The parallax effect is a captivating design technique that creates an illusion of depth in web pages. By moving background images at a different speed than foreground content, it draws users into the experience, making websites more interactive and engaging. This effect not only enhances visual appeal but also boosts user retention, leading to better overall performance.</p>
